text: The Copa México 1932–33 was the 17th staging of this Mexican football cup competition that existed from 1907. The competition started on June 18, 1933 and concluded on July 23, 1933 in which Necaxa lifted the trophy for third time after a 3-1 victory over Germania FV. ==Preliminary round== \---- ==Final Phase== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 auto;" |- !Copa México 1932-33 Winners |- |Necaxa 3rd Title |} ==References== *Mexico - Statistics of Copa México in season 1932/1933.
